WEBVTT

00:00:03.320 --> 00:00:05.879
Shahrukh Khan: Cricket. 
A gentleman’s game?

00:00:05.880 --> 00:00:07.660
A male pavilion? A boys' club?

00:00:08.250 --> 00:00:10.160
No, not any more.

00:00:10.160 --> 00:00:12.799
Recently at the Women’s
World Cup cricket final,

00:00:12.800 --> 00:00:16.079
our women’s cricket team showed the world

00:00:16.079 --> 00:00:21.519
that our girls are in no way lesser
than Virat Kohli and his boys.

00:00:21.520 --> 00:00:23.919
In a country where cricket
is a kind of religion,

00:00:23.920 --> 00:00:28.390
now it’s not just cricket gods
but even cricket goddesses who are rising.

00:00:28.390 --> 00:00:30.539
And today one of them